				h1.articleheading.sa-backgroundcolor who is SILICON ARTIST?
				p.articletext Steven always looked for easy money where he could find it - and found it in email scams, bank robberies & wire fraud. Everything was good until he robbed the wrong person. Kidnapped by hired goons and strapped to an operating table, Steven was injected with an experimental serum designed to turn human flesh in a pliable rubber. Steven became a horrible blob. Everything should have been different.

				p.articletext Troubled con artist and professional thief SILICON ARTIST is one of the newest members of Knox's Villain Underground criminal organization. Mastering his ability to stretch and shape his skin like clay, SILICON ARTIST loves to pester his opponents with insults and imitations for his own weird pleasure. While he may not be the most bloodthirsty member of the Viilain Underground, this invincible mess always seems to bounce back. 
		.row.articlerow
