						img.articlehorzimg.center-block(src="http://res.cloudinary.com/jhi5/image/upload/e_auto_contrast,q_54:420,r_25/v1498676135/ballooningbicep.jpg")
						h4.articleskilltext Ballooning Bicep is a Utility card available in Silicon Artist's deck. Played by itself, Ballooning Bicep sits in play. At the end of each turn, you may choose to destroy it in order to draw a card. 
					.col-md-6.articlecardpanel 
