						img.articlevertimg.center-block(src="http://res.cloudinary.com/jhi5/image/upload/e_auto_contrast,q_54:420,r_25/v1498676135/bodyrang.jpg")
						h4.articleskilltext Bodyrang is also an Action card available in Silicon Artist's deck. Played by itself, it deals 2 damage to any one player. You may also destroy one of your STRETCHED! cards in play to return it to your hand instead of placing it into the discard pile.
